data.description: Stunning spacious home located in the rural area of Mico TX. Just 12 miles from 1604 and Culebra. This beauty of a home is equipped with 5 bedrooms which of 2 are masters, as well as 4 and a half baths and a bonus space that can be used as a home theater, Workout, or Game room! It has awesome views from both balconies that give off vacation vibes. The home sits on a 10 acre property in a chain link fence with plenty of space and privacy to enjoy nature. There is no Home Owners Association.
